problem:
The following diagonal is drawn in a regular icosagon, creating an octadecagon and a quadrilateral.  What is the measure of $x$?

[asy]
import markers;
for(int i=0; i <=20; ++i) {
draw(dir(360*i/20+90)--dir(360*(i+1)/20+90));
}
pair A = dir(360*0/20+90);
pair F = dir(360*17/20+90);
pair G = dir(360*18/20+90);
pair H = dir(360*19/20+90);

draw(A--F);

markangle(Label("$x$",Relative(0.5)),n=1,radius=18,G,F,A);

[/asy]
